eto&amp;author=CI+Mandara&amp;volume=9&amp;publication_year=2007&amp;pages=38-43&amp;pmid=17547099&amp;" target="pmc_ext" ref="reftype=other&amp;article-id=2577657&amp;issue-id=161281&amp;journal-id=63&amp;FROM=Article%7CCitationRef&amp;TO=Content%20Provider%7CLink%7CGoogle%20Scholar">Google Scholar</a>]</span></span></li><li id="B10"><span class="citation">Hoa NP, Thorson AE, Long NH, Diwan VK. Knowledge of tuberculosis and associated health-seeking behaviour among rural Vietnamese adults with a cough for at least three weeks. <span><span class="ref-journal">Scand J Public Health Suppl. </span>2003;<span class="ref-vol">62</span>:59\xe2\x80\x9365. doi: 10.1080/14034950310015121.</span> [<a href="/pubmed/14649645" target="pmc_ext" ref="reftype=pubmed&amp;article-id=2577657&amp;issue-id=161281&amp;journal-id=63&amp;FROM=Article%7CCitationRef&amp;TO=Entrez%7CPubMed%7CRecord">PubMed</a>] [<a href="//dx.doi.org/10.1080%2F14034950310015121" target="pmc_ext" ref="reftype=other&amp;article-id=2577657&amp;issue-id=161281&amp;journal-id=63&amp;FROM=Article%7CCitationRef&amp;TO=Content%20Provider%7CCrosslink%7CDOI">CrossRef</a>] <span class="nowrap">[<a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?journal=Scand+J+Public+Health+Suppl&amp;title=Knowledge+of+tuberculosis+and+associated+health-seeking+behaviour+among+rural+Vietnamese+adults+with+a+cough+for+at+least+three+weeks&amp;author=NP+Hoa&amp;author=AE+Thorson&amp;author=NH+Long&amp;author=VK+Diwan&amp;volume=62&amp;publication_year=2003&amp;pages=59-65&amp;pmid=14649645&amp;doi=10.1080/14034950310015121&amp;" target="pmc_ext" ref="reftype=other&amp;article-id=2577657&amp;issue-id=161281&amp;journal-id=63&amp;FROM=Article%7CCitationRef&amp;TO=Content%20Provider%7CLink%7CGoogle%20Scholar">Google Scholar</a>]</span></span></li><li id="B11"><span class="citation">Agboatwalla M, Kazi GN, Shah SK, Tariq M. Gender perspectives on knowledge and practices regarding tuberculosis in urban and rural areas in Pakistan. <span><span 